N172 Roger Connor script series card, should grade a 3.5 and really nice.  SOLD

N172 Ned Williamson, NrMtMt all around but has a microscopic wear spot, should still grade a 5 or so.  $395

1897 Cedar Rapids Team composite cabinet stock photo.  Just about this entire team is in the Cameo Pepsin set and many are future/ex major leaguers.  Beautiful item.  $795

Original cyanotype photo of Theodore Kennedy (in the Old Judge set) in full uniform and pitching from about 1905 $295

(6) Cyanotype photos of Kennedy's pitching grips (1905), RARE series of original pitching progression photos with handwritten notations by Kennedy who died in 1907.  $150 each or $750 for all 6.  

Rhys Yeakley
